to compete in an epic tournament-styled hackathon.

The Pinnacle Design is focused around brevity, and guiding
the reader with purposeful lines. To create a design in line
with the Pinnacle aesthetic, the most important rule to follow
is to think of ways to leave out lines. By leaving gaps for the
reader, it creates mentally stimulating design while leading the
eyes towards the points that the designer wants to accentuate.
